data.description: Great, MOVE-IN READY Georgian-style home! Spacious kitchen w/ granite countertops, light cabinetry w/ soft closing drawers, & brand new SS dishwasher & microwave. Great family room w/ a wood burning fireplace, large windows, built-in bookshelves & a dry bar. The formal living room could also be a home office, flex room, or converted to a 5th bedroom. New LED, canned lighting throughout the downstairs. All the bathrooms have been beautifully renovated w/ calacatta gold quartz countertops, new fixtures, & custom-built, solid wood cabinetry with soft closing drawers. Upstairs are all 4 bedrooms. The primary bedroom has direct access to a secondary bedroom which can be used as a nursery, office, media room, or craft room. The exterior boasts an oversized backyard w/ plenty of space for a pool. New water heater-2023, New Carpet-2023, new HVAC-2021, New Hardy Plank-2017. ALL APPLIANCES STAY! Low tax rate & quick access to Beltway 8, 290, & 249. Zoned to Cy-Fair ISD. A must see!
